		<h2>SPOJ Problem Set (classical)</h2>
				<h1>10239. Between the Mountains</h1>
		<h2>Problem code: ACPC11B</h2>
	</td>
	</tr>
</table>

<p align="justify">
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 109px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;">Did you try to ride a telepherique (cable car)? It is a lot of fun. Our company is trying to</div>
